  <ItemGroup Condition=" '$(TargetFrameworkIdentifier)' == '.NETFramework' Or ('$(TargetFrameworkIdentifier)' == '.NETCoreApp' And '$(_TargetFrameworkVersionWithoutV)' &lt; '7.0')">
